          <div class="minicontainer">

            <h2 id="Driving-License" class="medium-main-title">> Driving Licences</h2> 
              <div class="content-container">
                <br>
                  
                <p class="normal-text">Learning to drive is common with many young adults. Most people can start learning to drive when they're 17. View more info through the button below:</p>
                <div>
                  <p id="learn-to-drive-info">
                    <a class="default-button" target="_blank" href="https://www.gov.uk/learn-to-drive-a-car">
                      <span class="more-info-text">More Info</span>
                      <svg class="apply-svg-graphic" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17.5" height="25" viewBox="0 0 33 34" focusable="false" aria-hidden="true"><path fill="currentColor" d="M0 0h13l20 20-20 20H0l20-20z"></path></svg>
                      <!---svg arrow on buttons [class="default-button"] courtesey of: "https://GOV.uk" website-->
                    </a>
                  </p>
                </div>

                <p class="normal-text">To start learning to drive, you must first obtain a provisional driving licence for a car, motorbike, moped or other vehicle from DVLA online.</p>
                  <br>
                <p class="normal-text">To apply you must:</p>
                  <br>
                <div class="normal-bulleted-text">
                  <ul>
                    <li class="individual-bullets">Be at least 15 years and 9 months old</li>
                    <li class="individual-bullets">Able to <a class="page-contents-media-link underlined-link" target="_blank" href="https://www.gov.uk/driving-eyesight-rules">read a number plate from 20 metres away</a></li>
                    <li class="individual-bullets">Have been given permission to live in Great Britain (England, Scotland and Wales) for at least 185 days</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
                
                <p class="normal-text">If you have already read all of the information, and know all the<a class="page-contents-media-link underlined-link" target="_blank" href="https://www.gov.uk/legal-obligations-drivers-riders"> requirements of driving a vehicle</a> on UK roads. Use the button below to apply for a provisional licence.</p>
                <div>
                  <p id="provisional-license-apply">
                    <a class="default-button" target="_blank" href="https://www.gov.uk/apply-first-provisional-driving-licence">
                      <span class="apply-here-text">Apply Here</span>
                      <svg class="apply-svg-graphic" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17.5" height="25" viewBox="0 0 33 34" focusable="false" aria-hidden="true"><path fill="currentColor" d="M0 0h13l20 20-20 20H0l20-20z"></path></svg>
                      <!---svg arrow on buttons [class="default-button"] courtesey of: "https://GOV.uk" website-->
                    </a>
                  </p>
                </div>

                <p class="normal-text">Another extremely useful government resource to review is the Highway Code, as this outlines all of the rules and regulations around driving. If new to the highway code, you can also view an<a class="page-contents-media-link underlined-link" target="_blank" href="https://www.gov.uk/guidance/the-highway-code/introduction"> introduction to this legislation.</a> Click the button below to view this, and the rules to follow of the Highway Code:</p>
                <div>
                  <p id="highway-code-link">
                    <a class="default-button" target="_blank" href="https://www.gov.uk/guidance/the-highway-code">
                      <span class="view-here-text">View Here</span>
                      <svg class="apply-svg-graphic" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17.5" height="25" viewBox="0 0 33 34" focusable="false" aria-hidden="true"><path fill="currentColor" d="M0 0h13l20 20-20 20H0l20-20z"></path></svg>
                      <!---svg arrow on buttons [class="default-button"] courtesey of: "https://GOV.uk" website-->
                    </a>
                  </p>
                </div>
           
              </div>
            <div class="horisontal-line-spacer"></div>



            <h2 id="Passport" class="medium-main-title">> Passports</h2> 
              <div class="content-container">
                  <br>
                <p class="normal-text">To venture abroad on holiday, you will be required to own a valid passport to do so.</p>
                  <br>
               
                <p class="normal-text">If you do not already own a valid passport, or an older one has expired, use button below to apply for a new British Passport online.</p>
                <div>
                  <p id="passport-apply">
                    <a class="default-button" target="_blank" href="https://www.gov.uk/apply-renew-passport">
                      <span class="apply-here-text">Apply Here</span>
                      <svg class="apply-svg-graphic" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17.5" height="25" viewBox="0 0 33 34" focusable="false" aria-hidden="true"><path fill="currentColor" d="M0 0h13l20 20-20 20H0l20-20z"></path></svg>
                      <!---svg arrow on buttons [class="default-button"] courtesey of: "https://GOV.uk" website-->
                    </a>
                  </p>
                </div>

                <p class="normal-text">If you wish to lean more about passports, change passport details, or access other passport related services, use the button below to do so. </p>
                <div>
                  <p id="passport-more-info">
                    <a class="default-button" target="_blank" href="https://www.gov.uk/browse/abroad/passports">
                      <span class="more-info-text">More Info</span>
                      <svg class="apply-svg-graphic" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17.5" height="25" viewBox="0 0 33 34" focusable="false" aria-hidden="true"><path fill="currentColor" d="M0 0h13l20 20-20 20H0l20-20z"></path></svg>
                      <!---svg arrow on buttons [class="default-button"] courtesey of: "https://GOV.uk" website-->
                    </a>
                  </p>
                </div>

              </div>  
            <div class="horisontal-line-spacer"></div>



            <h2 id="Voting" class="medium-main-title">> Voting Sign-Up</h2> 
              <div class="content-container">
                <br>
                
                <p class="normal-text">To get onto the electoral register, so that you can vote in elections or referendums, you will need to sign-up to vote first.</p>
                  <br>
                <p class="normal-text">To register to vote you must:</p>
                  <br>
                    <div class="normal-bulleted-text">
                      <ul>
                        <li class="individual-bullets">Be aged 16 or over (or 14 or over in Scotland and Wales).</li>
                      </ul>
                    </div>
                <p class="normal-text">You normally only need to register once - not for every election. You'll need to register again if you've changed your name, address or nationality. </p>
                  <br>
                <p class="normal-text">To get more information on the registration process, and also sign-up to vote, use the button below:</p>
                
                <div>
                  <p id="voting-signup-button">
                    <a class="default-button" target="_blank" href="https://www.gov.uk/register-to-vote">
                      <span class="more-info-text">More Info</span>
                      <svg class="apply-svg-graphic" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17.5" height="25" viewBox="0 0 33 34" focusable="false" aria-hidden="true"><path fill="currentColor" d="M0 0h13l20 20-20 20H0l20-20z"></path></svg>
                      <!---svg arrow on buttons [class="default-button"] courtesey of: "https://GOV.uk" website-->
                    </a>
                  </p>
                </div>

              </div>
            <div class="horisontal-line-spacer"></div>



            <h2 id="NHS-Website" class="medium-main-title">> NHS website and Services</h2> 
              <div class="content-container">
                <br>
                  <p class="normal-text">The NHS Website contains lots of helpful information around health and wellbeing.</p>
                <br>
                  <p class="normal-text">It is an essential tool to use, especially for young adults arranging appointments or other NHS services themselves for the first time, as opposed to asking parents to do so on their behalf. </p>
                
                <div>
                  <p id="nhs-website-link">
                    <a class="default-button" target="_blank" href="https://www.nhs.uk/">
                      <span class="view-here-text">View Here</span>
                      <svg class="apply-svg-graphic" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17.5" height="25" viewBox="0 0 33 34" focusable="false" aria-hidden="true"><path fill="currentColor" d="M0 0h13l20 20-20 20H0l20-20z"></path></svg>
                      <!---svg arrow on buttons [class="default-button"] courtesey of: "https://GOV.uk" website-->
                    </a>
                  </p>
                </div>

                <p class="normal-text">In addition, many young-adults will have to start booking their own GP appointments for any health issues they may face. This is not a complicated process, and can now even be done through the NHS website or app, phone E-Consults are avaliable also for fast consultation with your doctor. Use the button below to view all the relevant information involved with booking a GP appointment:</p>
                <div>
                  <p id="gp-appointments-button">
                    <a class="default-button" target="_blank" href="https://www.nhs.uk/nhs-services/gps/gp-appointments-and-bookings/">
                      <span class="more-info-text">More Info</span>
                      <svg class="apply-svg-graphic" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17.5" height="25" viewBox="0 0 33 34" focusable="false" aria-hidden="true"><path fill="currentColor" d="M0 0h13l20 20-20 20H0l20-20z"></path></svg>
                      <!---svg arrow on buttons [class="default-button"] courtesey of: "https://GOV.uk" website-->
                    </a>
                  </p>
                </div>

                <p class="normal-text">If you are not already registered with a General-Practicioner(GP) doctor, use the button below to register with a local GP. It is important to do so, especially for discussing any future health issues that may require a GP doctor:</p>
                <div>
                  <p id="gp-signup-button">
                    <a class="default-button" target="_blank" href="https://www.nhs.uk/nhs-services/gps/how-to-register-with-a-gp-surgery/">
                      <span class="more-info-text">More Info</span>
                      <svg class="apply-svg-graphic" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17.5" height="25" viewBox="0 0 33 34" focusable="false" aria-hidden="true"><path fill="currentColor" d="M0 0h13l20 20-20 20H0l20-20z"></path></svg>
                      <!---svg arrow on buttons [class="default-button"] courtesey of: "https://GOV.uk" website-->
                    </a>
                  </p>
                </div>

              </div>
            <div class="horisontal-line-spacer"></div>



            <h2 id="git-repo-message" class="medium-main-title">> Another Government Service...</h2> 
              <div class="content-container">
                <br>
                  <p class="normal-text">This website is completely modular, and allows for additional government services to be added that are very useful for young-adults to be aquanted with.</p>
                <br>
                  <p class="normal-text">It would be incredibly useful for young-people to have a dedicated GOV.uk hub with all government services in one place, as it is much easier to search a single webpage than multiple government websites.</p>
                <br>
                  <p class="normal-text">To view a copy of the HTML and CSS code used to create this site, and review the modularity of the code, use the button below to visit it's dedicated GitHub Repository.</p>

